{"tid":598459,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"［點睇］泰漢稱獲靈童報夢「畀料」　買132張彩票全中","createTime":"2018-03-19T13:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T13:41:18.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ea32744c431466cebf5024a19f121a0566a9b3ee","tid":598459,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/213645_58929c2c47e6232688b7cc36ba500333.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F213645_58929c2c47e6232688b7cc36ba500333.png&h=20123050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西提猜（右）稱獲靈童報夢，助他贏得獎金。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n不少人都會買彩劵一碰運氣，希望獲得意外之財。泰國一名男子近日聲稱，自己獲得靈童「古曼童」報夢，並按着靈童的「貼士」購入132張彩票，結果全部中獎，一共贏得26.4萬泰銖（約6.6萬港元）的彩金。<br />\n<br />\n據當地媒體報道，來自大城府的西提猜（Sitthichai Yoddamnone）聲稱自己早前得到泰國靈童「古曼童」報夢，夢到「82」這個數字。西提猜醒來後又問了在「古曼童」神像旁玩耍的3歲孫子，「彩券會開出哪個號碼」，他的孫子竟然也回答82。<br />\n<br />\n西提猜隨即走遍多個地區，花費了10560泰銖（2655港元）購入每張價值為80泰銖（約20港元）的彩票，它們的尾碼均為「82」。彩票在上周五開彩，西提猜也料不到會全部中獎，令他一夜致富。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180319/mobile/bknint-20180319102123748-0319_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180319%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20180319102123748-0319_17011_001.html&d=%2BP4PBHkQFZevcBQJktJHTzACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=8b15f5a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180319/mobile/bknint-20180319102123748-0319_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"56e628c243d1141964788ac1800a2d8b60f415ad","tid":598459,"uid":77569,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:39:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6969a73d6e62a316e92e899f133a005f035bf35c","tid":598459,"uid":17838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T13:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先得果6萬6"},{"pid":"be2629428ca24ed9a18cceebf9bd47c48ba54f62","tid":598459,"uid":14624